item.title: CVE-2023-39519|2024-10-02T18:30:35.519Z -- cloudexplorer-dev -- cloudexplorer-lite
item.description: Cloud Explorer Lite is an open source cloud management platform. Prior to version 1.4.0, there is a risk of sensitive information leakage in the user information acquisition of CloudExplorer Lite. The vulnerability has been fixed in version 1.4.0.
